          <p class="book-font-2">
            Skip the lines, no waiting. Doorbell Barbers comes to you, on your
            schedule and your time. Our barbers use a portable floor mat.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="select-button">
          <a href="customer_select_barber.jsp"
